Portugal-German 10-Year Yield Spread Climbs to a Record Basis 568 Points

-- B y   E m m a   C h a r l t o n
-- 
2011-04-18T07:59:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-18/portugal-german-10-year-yield-spread-climbs-to-a-record-basis-568-points.html
The yield difference, or spread,
between German 10-year bunds and Portuguese securities of a
similar maturity widened to 568 basis points as of 8:58 a.m. in
 London , the most since at least 1998, when Bloomberg began
collecting data.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emma Charlton in London at 
 echarlton1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Keith Campbell at 
 k.campbell@bloomberg.net  